snippet.title: Forested Super Mario Bros. U - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Forested Super Mario Bros. U!

This mod was originally an idea by WillyMaker used to hide his bigger project: Super Mario Evolution.
After talking with him about it, we decided to make this mod a reality!

Forested Super Mario Bros. U will contain:
- 1 world
- 8 different fun foresty levels
- Custom music
- Brand new backgrounds and tilesets
And so much more!

Download link: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1uwE-s8h-eZm7QKHaX73joiOhJ04EkJ7B?usp=sharing

We are not affiliated with Nintendo, and all Nintendo characters such as Mario, Luigi, Toad, and others belong to Nintendo.
We do not endorse or support piracy.
